storyTitle: Tom and Jerry Get the cheese
storyEntry: jerry runs away from tom and then tom catches jerry and beats him up. then tom takes the cheese back and says don't touch my cheese. - sami

Today, some guy punched me square in the face for bullying him through high school. I had no idea who he was, and he was angrily yelling for what I once did to him in teacher X's class. I never had teacher X. Then he realised we didn’t even go to the same school. Mistaken identity = my busted nose.

storyTitle: Shrek is love, Shrek is life
storyEntry: One day there was a ogre called Shrek. He said get out of my swamp, Donkehhh! Then the noble steed replied "You're like an onion". This story doesn't make any sense.

One of my wife’s third graders was wearing a Fitbit watch, which prompted my wife to ask, “Are you tracking your steps?” “No,” said the little girl. “I wear this for Mommy so she can show Daddy when he gets home.”
